org.ipdr.protocol
Class ProtocolData

java.lang.Object
  org.ipdr.protocol.ProtocolData
Direct Known Subclasses:
ProtocolDataBigEndian
public abstract class ProtocolData
extends java.lang.Object

Various methods for getting data from IPDR/CRANE records and putting data into IPDR/CRANE records. Most of these methods are abstract, allowing for big-endian and little-endian implementations.
